Alexia Christian was shot dead by police in downtown Atlanta on Thursday . 
  She was allegedly sitting in the back of a patrol car when she fired at least two shots at officers . 
  The incident happened near the Fulton County Courthouse on Thursday afternoon . 
  Police were investigating a call about a stolen car and took her into custody . 
  At one point she allegedly fired at the officers and they returned fire . 
  The woman has been identified as 25-year-old Alexia Christian . 
 